CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, page 21, reads: "The Courier Home Service Grand Prize Window... winners of the Beacon Furniture Company 60-piece set of Verde Moderna Dinnerware are, left to right, Daisy Reynold, Ethel Prysock and A. Velar... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Harry Waugh handing box of Philco 60 piece set of Verde Moderne dinnerware to Daisy Reynold, Ethel Prysock ,and A. Velar,  standing in front of stage in Hunt Armory at the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
